Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 呐 小鸠 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 给我念念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(萤火虫之光 作 森飒太郎 画 新村奈绪子)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 念念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠难不成不会念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会念的啦

Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:44.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:44.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}该怎么办才好来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:49.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:49.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所当然的事情总是这么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:52.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:52.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}纷繁复杂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:55.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:55.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想开心的时候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:01:00.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:01:00.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的时候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:08.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:08.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常说愿望总会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:16.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:16.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是总会到底要多久　已经等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:19.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:19.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:21.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:21.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}张开双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:30.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:30.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告诉我在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:33.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:33.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:36.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:36.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}伤得满目疮痍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:39.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:39.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:43.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:43.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}几十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:46.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:46.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是这样还
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:50.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:50.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}难以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:54.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:54.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信着明天

